#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/animation.rst:1
msgid ""
"KDE, Kdenlive, add clips, animation, editing, timeline, documentation, user "
"manual, video editor, open source, free, learn, easy"
msgstr ""
"KDE, Kdenlive, afegir clips, animació, edició, línia de temps, documentació, "
"manual d'usuari, editor de vídeo, codi lliure, lliure, aprendre, fàcil"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/animation.rst:29
msgid "Create Animation"
msgstr "Creació d'animació"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/animation.rst:33
msgid ""
"Right-click on empty space in the project bin, or click the |kdenlive-add-"
"clip|\\ |go-down|\\ :guilabel:`Add Clip` icon on the project bin toolbar, "
"and select :guilabel:`Create Animation`."
msgstr ""
"Feu clic amb el botó dret en un espai buit a la safata del projecte, o "
"cliqueu la icona |kdenlive-add-clip|\\ |go-down|\\ :guilabel:`Afegeix un "
"clip` a la barra d'eines de la safata del projecte i seleccioneu :guilabel:"
"`Crea una animació`."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/animation.rst:36
#| msgid ""
#| "This requires |glaxnimate| to be installed and the path to it configured "
#| "in Kdenlive's :doc:`settings</user_interface/menu/settings_menu/"
#| "configure_kdenlive>`."
msgid ""
"This requires |glaxnimate| to be installed and the path to it configured in "
"Kdenlive's :ref:`settings<configure_environment_default_apps>`."
msgstr ""
"Això requereix que el |glaxnimate| estigui instal·lat i el seu camí "
"configurat a l':ref:`arranjament<configure_environment_default_apps>` del "
"Kdenlive."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/animation.rst:44
msgid "Creating an animation"
msgstr "Crear una animació"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/animation.rst:46
msgid ""
"This opens a dialog window to enter a name for the :file:`.rawr` file "
"Kdenlive creates before opening Glaxnimate."
msgstr ""
"Això obre una finestra de diàleg per a introduir un nom per al fitxer :file:"
"`.rawr` que el Kdenlive crea abans d'obrir el Glaxnimate."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/animation.rst:48
msgid ""
"If Glaxnimate is not configured, you are presented with a dialog box to "
"enter the path to Glaxnimate."
msgstr ""
"Si el Glaxnimate no està configurat, se us presentarà un quadre de diàleg "
"per a introduir el camí al Glaxnimate."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/animation.rst:52
msgid ""
"You can edit the animation in Glaxnimate by double-clicking on the animation "
"in the project bin, or by right-clicking and selecting :guilabel:`Edit Clip`."
msgstr ""
"Podeu editar l'animació en el Glaxnimate fent un doble clic a l'animació a "
"la safata del projecte, o amb un clic dret i seleccionat :guilabel:`Edita el "
"clip`."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/animation.rst:54
msgid ""
"For further details about editing an animation see the chapter :doc:`/"
"titles_and_graphics/graphics_and_animations/glaxnimate`."
msgstr ""
"Per a detalls addicionals sobre editar una animació, vegeu el capítol :doc:`/"
"titles_and_graphics/graphics_and_animations/glaxnimate`."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/animation.rst:56
msgid ""
"Kdenlive supports the :file:`Json` (Lottie animations) and :file:`rawr` "
"(Glaxnimate animation) file formats."
msgstr ""
"El Kdenlive admet els formats de fitxer :file:`Json` (animacions del Lottie) "
"i :file:`rawr` (animació del Glaxnimate)."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/animation.rst:58
msgid ""
":file:`Json` and :file:`rawr` files contain an alpha channel, so the "
"imported animations can be overlayed over other clips in the timeline."
msgstr ""
"Els fitxers :file:`Json` i :file:`rawr` contenen un canal alfa, així que les "
"animacions importades es poden superposar sobre altres clips a la línia de "
"temps."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/animation.rst:60
#| msgid ""
#| "For Glaxnimate installation see the chapter about :ref:`default_apps`."
msgid ""
"For Glaxnimate installation see the chapter about :ref:"
"`configure_environment_default_apps`."
msgstr ""
"Per a la instal·lació del Glaxnimate, vegeu el capítol sobre :ref:"
"`configure_environment_default_apps`."
